{
  "text": "And well there are two concepts with which you deal. The first is the great way of the development of the light in the microcosmic mind, body, spirit. It is assume that an adept will have its energy centers functioning smoothly and in a balanced manner to its best effort before a magical working, all magical workings are based upon evocation and invocation the first invocation of any magical working is that invocation of the magical personality as you are familiar with this term in the working of which you speak. Since you do not have an item of apparel or talisman, the gesture which you have made is appropriate. The second station is the evocation of the Great Cross of Life. This is an extension of the magical personality, to become be creator again, all invocations and evocations are drawn through the violet energy center.",
